Context is great for low frequency updates, but not for high updates 

> User authentication is not going to chang eoften, so you can use context-api 
> A high frequency update for, for exmaple an element that is constantly changing
> Every component that uses usecontext will be updated, even if its not being affected 
> It's great for some things, but not for everything


There is a different way to have a global store by building a custom hook for it 
